creator: MDK Technologies LTD
descriptionHtml:
MDK is a place where people gather around thematic boards and create new ideas and discussions.

Join the boards you are interested in to create your personalized feed of content like people's stories, hot discussions, news, games, fresh memes or funny videos.

Publish posts, share your opinions or your own works and get feedback from people with similar interests. On MDK, you don’t have to have a lot of followers to be heard. If people like your post, it will automatically fall into the hot stream, where thousands of users will see it.

Rate other people's posts and decide which ones deserve more attention. There is no editorial policy on MDK – all content is created and ranked by users themselves.

Get our coins for your activity on the platform and spend them to support your favorite authors, promote posts or create new boards.
descriptionShort: Thematic boards

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Slightly more options for board moderators. You'll like it.

title: MAIN: online community

creator: MDK Technologies LTD
descriptionHtml:
MAIN is a new type of crypto social network owned and operated by its users.

On MAIN, you can:
- Do everything the same as in other social networks: comment, make posts, vote for the content, create your own communities or join existing ones.
- Get MAIN tokens for your activity on the platform or as rewards from other users. Tokens are distributed every day to all MAIN users.
- Buy coins of any communities on the platform and take part in their management or earn on their growth.
- Withdraw tokens from the platform and exchange them for other cryptocurrencies.

On MAIN, you don't need to have followers to get noticed. If other people like your post, the feed algorithms will automatically bring it to the very top.

MAIN has no real names and no connection to your personality, so here you can be yourself and not be afraid to say what you think.
descriptionShort: A social media platform operated and owned by its users

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:

Added a list of favorite boards and the ability to report posts that break board rules.

- Do everything the same as in other social networks: comment, make posts, vote for the content, create your own communities or join existing ones.
- Get MAIN tokens for your activity on the platform or as rewards from other users. Tokens are distributed every day to all MAIN users.
- Buy coins of any communities on the platform and take part in their management or earn on their growth.
- Withdraw tokens from the platform and exchange them for other cryptocurrencies.

On MAIN, you don't need to have followers to get noticed. If other people like your post, the feed algorithms will automatically bring it to the very top.

MAIN has no real names and no connection to your personality, so here you can be yourself and not be afraid to say what you think.
